org.gvsig.gpe.xml.stream
Class AbstractXmlStreamReaderWrapper

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.gpe.xml.stream.AbstractXmlStreamReaderWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
IXmlStreamReader
public abstract class AbstractXmlStreamReaderWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements IXmlStreamReader

Plain wrapper for an IXmlStreamReader aimed at easying the creation of IXmlStreamReader decorators.

This class is a pure abstract wrapper, so all methods delegate to the wrapped object.

Version:
